Add suspend/resume support for HTVEC irqchip, which is needed for
suspend/hibernation.

Signed-off-by: Huacai Chen <chenhuacai@loongson.cn>
Signed-off-by: Jianmin Lv <lvjianmin@loongson.cn>
---
